---
title: Sweet and Sticky Korean Style Chicken Stir-Fry with Pepper, Onion and Jasmine Rice
description: Looking for a quick and tasty midweek dinner option? Try cooking up our Sweet and Sticky Korean Style Chicken Stir-Fry in just 20 minutes for a delicious and speedy meal.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R07_W36_UK_QR15735-4_Main__1low-501a3dc9.jpg
